shotcomp.shot_size_description: The video shows a street scene with a person with pink hair, glasses, and a black mask positioned on the far left of the frame. Only part of their upper body is visible, taking up about 10% of the frame's width.

The video shows a street scene. It begins with a wide shot of the road, then pans left to reveal a person with pink hair, glasses, and a black mask, shown from the chest up on the right. On the left, a man in light clothing is seen picking up a phone from the ground.

The video shows a street scene with two people. It starts with a person with pink hair, glasses, and a black mask, whose chest-up body occupies 50% of the right side of the frame's height. On the left, a person in light clothes is bent down, with their full body occupying less than 50% of the frame's height. The camera then pans right, leaving the pink-haired person in the lower left corner, revealing more of the street.

The video mainly shows a street scene, with humans included. Initially, a person with pink hair, glasses, and a black mask shows their shoulders and above. The camera then pans left, revealing the full body of a man in light-colored clothing.

The video opens with a medium shot, showing the back of a curly-haired figure with a backpack walking in the foreground, while a man holding a book approaches from the background. A third figure then enters the scene as all three walk toward each other in a hallway. The curly-haired figure and another person with long dark hair are seen from behind, with the man holding the book partially visible between them.

The video takes place in a street block environment with two people. It starts with a black screen, likely due to one person being too close to the camera. The camera then moves, revealing the surroundings, part of a person's body, and the back of the other person ahead.

The video begins with a full shot of a woman arching in a soccer field. As the camera moves backward, it becomes apparent that the scene is within a picture frame that appears to move. The camera continues to pull back, revealing the picture frame resting on a small table in a bedroom.

This low-angle shot shows a girl sitting on a chair, taking sneakers out of a bag. The frame is cluttered with multiple human subjects, and the bag in the foreground partially occludes the girl's body. Overall, it appears to capture most of her body in a full shot.

A man investigates a yellow pipe, inserting his finger and triggering a surreal journey through its twists and turns. The camera pulls back to reveal the pipe's intricate path, culminating in a startling encounter with glowing orange eyes and a chilling fade to crimson.

The video is filmed in a restaurant, showing a pair of wrinkled hands with rings and bracelets in first-person POV. Across the table, a man rests his head on his arms while extending his index finger. There are drinks and leftover food on the dining table.

The video shows a person lying on a sofa, with their feet positioned closer to the camera and their head farther away. The shallow focus emphasizes the feet, adorned with shiny sprinkles, while the rest of the body is slightly blurred. The composition divides the frame, with the lower half featuring the person on the sofa and the upper half showcasing empty space.
An over-the-shoulder shot shows a girl's head in the foreground, out of focus, seemingly watching a man in the middle ground, who is in focus and framed in a medium shot, lifting weights.

The camera is mounted on the car's front, facing inside the vehicle through the windshield. There are four passengers in the vehicle, with their chest-up bodies visible. It overall creates a medium shot, even though most of their upper bodies are hidden by the vehicle.

The video shows a man in orange clothing, wearing sunglasses and a hat, in an urban street scene. The shot begins with the man’s body from the knees up, occupying only 30% of the frame, leaving more content for the surroundings. The camera then moves closer, gradually increasing his size in the frame, until it focuses on a close-up of him.

This frame shows a man in the driver’s seat, filmed through the car's windshield. Only his head and part of his shoulder are visible, with the rest hidden by the car. The background includes buildings, trees, and cars, suggesting an urban setting. The text "Malcolm X (1992)" appears at the bottom.

The video is set in a room, featuring a seated person and a cylindrical structure with circular holes emitting rotating spotlights in front of them. It begins with the camera positioned behind the person, capturing their chest-up body and the entire cylindrical structure. The camera then moves in a 180-degree semi-circular arc around the cylindrical structure until it obscures most of the person's body.

The video shows a restaurant scene with many customers. It begins with a medium close-up shot of a man eating noodles, with waitstaff and other diners in the background. The camera quickly pans left, revealing a robotic vacuum cleaner on the floor, surrounded by the dining area with many diners seated at tables.

The video starts by showing a lazy susan’s surface with no food items in focus. It then rotates to reveal various food items in a full shot, pausing on each one for a few seconds before moving to the next.

The video begins by showcasing a collection of banknotes and coins. The camera moves along the direction of the money and coins, gradually transitioning to a sculpture-like object. It continues to move, sequentially revealing three stone-like objects, ultimately coming to a stop on a full shot of one of the stones.

The video shows a man in red lying down, one hand supporting his head and the other holding a leg, exposing his foot's sole. On the left, a hand inspects his foot, while a man in blue sits on the right. Initially, only the blue man's head is visible at the bottom, but as the camera tilts down, it gradually reveals more parts of both men's bodies.

The video shows a hospital-like setting with a person in red lying on a hospital bed, one leg wrapped in bandages and suspended in the air. The video is filmed from behind a person in green, whose upper body appears in the foreground, partially blocking the upper body of the person in red.
The video begins with a black screen before transitioning to a wide shot of a house, where a man is seen walking toward it.

This video shows a person's upper body, from the chest up, trapped in the ceiling. The camera is positioned in a third-person over-the-shoulder view, shooting from the left behind of another person. Only a small portion of the person’s body and head are visible in the frame. The focus is on the person trapped in the ceiling, who is wearing a blue tie and holding a notebook in his right hand. His body is visible from the mid-thigh up to below the chest.

The video shows a home setting where a human head emerges through a blue carpet, taking up one-third of the frame's height and positioned slightly left of center. Wooden sticks are scattered on the carpet, with part of a sofa in the top right corner and part of a wooden chest of drawers in the top left corner.

The video shows a woman in a bathtub filled with foam, making her body below her head invisible beneath the foam. Her head occupies about one-third of the frame's height and is positioned to the right of the center.

This video consists of two separate clips, each taking up half of the screen and showing two scenes of people talking on the phone. On the left, the scene features a woman in military uniform, shown in a full shot. She is sitting on a chair with her legs propped up on the table, holding a red, vintage telephone while speaking. On the right, in a bathroom, a man in a yellow sweater is talking on a blue telephone. Three other people are visible on the left, acting anxious. As the shower curtain in the background is pulled back, another person’s head appears from inside the shower room, looking at them.
The video shows a full shot of a television screen, displaying a close-up of a woman driving, seen from the front. As the camera zooms in, she appears larger in the frame.

The video opens with a wide shot of a neoclassical domed building surrounded by ornate columns. The camera swiftly dollies forward and tilts upward, focusing on a statue of a man atop the triangular pediment.

The video shows a wide shot of a person dressed in white standing with their back to the camera in front of a large screen that nearly fills the frame. The screen displays a close-up of a woman’s face.

The video is shot from behind and to the right of a person, showing a boy in a striped t-shirt. At the start, it is a medium shot of the boy facing the camera, with a small portion of the person's arm visible on the left side of the frame. As the person moves forward, his body covers the boy, and by the end, only part of the person's arm and back are visible.
The video captures the person’s chest-up body, with only his hand clearly holding a small brown object in the foreground, and the rest of his body is blurred in the middle ground.
The scene is initially black, and after a few seconds, it becomes clear, revealing a setting that includes an umbrella stand and some photos.

The beginning of the video shows a stadium, with the camera following a few team members from behind as they walk. Only the upper bodies of these people are visible, occupying 30% of the frame's height, leaving more context for the surroundings. At the end of the video is a medium close-up shot of the last member of the team.
The camera begins with a full shot of a woman hanging in the air, clinging to a garment. It then tilts upward to reveal a man in a full shot holding the garment, emphasizing its strength.

The video shows a woman in a brightly colored outfit clinging to a large rock, her body suspended in mid-air with only her upper body visible. Behind her, two men hang one after another, partially visible in the frame. The video, shot from above, highlights the extreme height of their location, surrounded by towering mountains and dense clouds.
The video opens with an abstract blurry medium shot of bubbles underwater. It then cuts abruptly to a slow-motion wide shot of a male figure diving into the water, captured upside down.
The video begins with a black screen. Then, a close-up of a hand holding a stick appears. After a moment, the screen fades to black again.
The video begins with a black screen, followed by a close-up shot showing what seems to be a supporting leg of an object on a carpet.

The video features a man playing the drums, with a part of the drum set visible. The shot size transitions from a medium close-up of the man to a medium shot and then returns to a medium close-up at the end.

The video shows a woman in front of a mirror. She is on the right side of the frame, with only her profile from the shoulders up visible. The mirror is on the left side of the frame, reflecting her face. However, as she moves, her face eventually disappears from the mirror.

This video shows a small boat approaching a large ship. The camera, positioned on the large ship, captures the small boat in the sea with five people on board. As the boat gets closer, the camera pans right to track it, revealing part of the large ship and a person on deck.

The video shows a small boat approaching a larger ship at sea. The camera is set on the larger ship and shows the small boat with five people onboard. The right side of the frame also reveals part of the larger ship and the person on it.

The shot initially shows a person on a stretcher walking uphill from the side. Suddenly, it switches to the selfie perspective of the person on the stretcher, revealing half of his body and the upper body of the person pushing the stretcher.

The shot is taken from in front of the car's windshield. The car is driving through a city street at night, with buildings and streetlights visible in the background. Four people are seated in the car, with only their upper bodies visible. The two people in the back seat are partially obscured by the two in the front.

The video shows a man wearing sunglasses sitting in the back seat of a car, with his body visible from the shoulders up through the open car window. He is looking at the camera, with a blurred building and two people in the background.
The video begins with a wide shot of a man standing on a balcony, captured from a low angle. The camera swiftly tilts down to reveal a group of people below
The video shows a wide shot of a laundry room with two people in the center, the pink text title "KODAK ONHA" shows up and covers part of two people, which was added in post-production.

The video is shot from a first-person, high-angle view, showing a pair of hands and a man. The left hand holds a comb, and the right hand holds scissors. The man, dressed in an orange outfit, faces the camera and performs a rap, backing away as the camera moves forward.

The video shows a small orange ball entering the water. Initially, only the glass of water is visible, with no ball. As the ball enters the glass, it appears with a dynamic size, sometimes fully visible and other times only half visible. Overall, it's a full shot of the subject with dynamic size.

The video shows a slow-motion shot of a Black woman walking down the street, with a dynamic shot size due to her movement. It starts with a medium shot of her upper body, and as she gets closer to the camera, the shot transitions to a close-up. After she puts on sunglasses, she walks out of the frame.

The video shows a first-person perspective of a person at a concert. The crowd in front of the viewer jumps up and down, with their arms raised in the air, partially blocking the stage view as the lighting shifts between blue and red.

The video shows a red bag placed at the entrance of a closed apartment door, with a cardboard box on top of it. Then, a full shot of a man opening the apartment door, going out, picking up the cardboard box, then going back into the apartment and closing the door. Shortly after, another man walks into the frame from the right, picks up the bag at the entrance of the apartment.

The video shows a man in white clothes and jeans, carrying a red takeaway bag. It begins with a shot of his body up to half of his lower legs. As he walks to the right, half of his head exits the frame, and his body gradually takes up less space in the frame until only a small portion of his back and hips remain at the far right.

The video begins with a medium close-up shot of a man in a blue shirt in a kitchen. He appears to be placing a paper food container into an unseen spot below the frame. The camera follows the man, then pans left, leaving about half of his chest up body visible. On the left side of the frame, a small portion of another person's body and face becomes visible.
The video opens with a broad view of kites soaring in a pale sky. A hand occasionally enters the frame, holding a kite reel, suggesting a first-person perspective.

The shot initially focuses on the kite in the sky, presented as a scenery shot. Then, the camera tilts down and pans to the right, shifting to the child flying the kite. The child is shown with dynamic size and finally ends with a full shot of the child.

The video shows an open-air stadium during a game, with the stands filled with spectators. The camera is positioned in the stand, initially showing the field and the stands opposite. It then pans to the right, showing some people in the foreground at the frame's right corner, along with parts of the field and distant stands.

The video shows an outdoor sports stadium during a game, with the stands full of spectators. The camera is positioned among the audience. At the start, the foreground shows a medium shot of some spectators from the left rear of them, occupying the lower left corner of the frame. The remaining space shows a more distant view of the stands and the stadium. The camera then pans left, showing a wider view of the stadium and the opposite stands.
The video maintains a medium close-up shot of a woman tying the fence. The fence is positioned in front of her, partially blocking her face, shoulders, and arms, so they are not always fully visible.

The shot beings with a full shot of two characters, before one hits the other with a flaming punch. The camera tilts and pans to track him as he is launched into the air, before ending on a full shot of him standing up in the snow.

The video features a close-up shot of a human figure wearing a hood and a yellow mask. The camera maintains a level angle, focusing tightly on the upper part of the character's face and mask. As the scene progresses, the figure is struck by a glassy object, causing it to shatter into many pieces.

The video begins with a wide shot of a group of hockey players celebrating near the rink boards, with a crowd of spectators visible in the background. As the camera slowly zooms in, the focus shifts to the players, tightening the frame.

The video is filmed from a drone POV and shows a monster being attacked by tanks. It begins with a slightly blurry view of a rooftop and a small portion of the monster in focus at the top of the frame. As the drone moves forward, the full body of the monster is revealed, along with tanks nearby firing at it.

The drone shot begins with a wide view of a hot air balloon. As the drone approaches, the balloon's top gradually fills the frame until only the top is visible. After crossing over the balloon, the view transitions to a snow-covered ground, eventually revealing white subtitle text in the frame.

The shot begins with a medium shot of the front section of a Porsche from the side. The camera then moves backward to reveal a full front view of the car, before circling to the opposite side and transitioning back into a medium shot. Finally, it transitions to a full shot of the car, filmed from its right rear side.

The video begins with a full shot of a race car from behind. As the car slows to turn, the camera begins to move in front of the car, capturing it with a medium shot. The video ends with a full shot of the race car, from the front.

The video shows a boat moving in the sea. It begins with a view of the sea, where only a small part of the red boat appears in the upper-right corner. The camera then tilts upward and pans left, following the boat’s movement until the entire boat comes into frame.

The video shows an escalator scene, with the camera positioned on an ascending escalator, filming from behind a person. Only the person's upper body above the chest is visible, taking up half the height of the frame, leaving more content for the surroundings.
A wide shot of a city street, with the camera following a woman from behind as she walks. The video only shows the upper body of the woman, leaving more context for the street scenery.

The video captures crocodiles in a lake from the shore. The crocodile close to the camera has about half of its body above the water, occupying 60% of the frame's width, with the rest submerged. In the distance, another crocodile is visible, with only a small portion of its body above the water.

The video is filmed behind a woman on a balcony, showing her throwing paper outside. The background features many people on a construction site in the opposite building. The woman is blurred, with her upper body visible, occupying 70% of the frame's height. The shot emphasizes her motion of throwing the paper, but the focus is on the people in the background.

The video is shot from a third-person over-the-shoulder POV on a balcony, showing a man and woman, and people on the opposite balcony. It starts by focusing on the people across, with the foreground blurry, showing half of the upper body of a man in white and a woman in gray blue from behind. The woman then turns, and the focus shifts to her as she kisses the man.

The video features a group of policemen standing together. The people in the foreground are shown only from the face, those in the middle are framed from the waist up, and the people in the background are shown in full body, though some are partially occluded by others in front.
The video starts with a wide shot of a street scene with some people. The camera then pans right to focus on a sign with a scenery picture.

The video begins with a street-side sign displaying information about fortune telling, with part of a bicycle visible on the left. The camera then pans left, revealing the entrance of a ramen restaurant and a person walking out. The pan continues, showing more people on the street, but with no clear focus, primarily capturing the overall scene. The entire shot is a wide shot.

The video shows a passenger boat on a river. It begins with an extreme wide shot from above and behind the boat. The camera then arcs around it while descending in altitude. The video ends with a wide shot from the front, showing the boat’s bow and a person seated there.
The video shows a frog climbing a metal rod. It starts with a close-up of the rod, then the frog enters from the bottom left, climbs up, and stops at the center of the frame, shown in a full shot.

The video begins with a full shot of a white leather shoe with a belt draped over it. A frog then appears from the bottom left, crawling on the belt. The camera tracks the frog as it moves left, and finally, the frog jumps to the ground.

The video starts with a full shot of a handgun, with two bullets in the foreground. A butterfly then flies across the frame. After that, a frog jumps onto the gun's trigger, stays for a moment, and jumps out of the frame.

The video begins with a close-up shot, focusing on a small water sprayer in the foreground, fully in frame. The focus then shifts (rack focus) to three frogs in the middleground, which jump into the frame one by one.

The shot begins with a medium shot of the front section of a Porsche from the side. The camera then moves backward to reveal a full front view of the car, before circling to the opposite side and transitioning back into a medium shot. Finally, it transitions to a full shot of the car, filmed from its right rear side.

The video takes place in a desert surrounding. In the beginning, the camera moves closer to two camels and a person, then quickly passes over them, revealing a car speeding through the desert, kicking up a large amount of sand. The camera then approaches the flying sand, transitioning into a slow-motion shot of sand and debris flying toward the camera, creating a powerful scene.

The scene begins with a full shot of a man on a bicycle. As he approaches the camera, he becomes bigger in the frame and finally exits the frame from the bottom right corner. The camera keeps moving up, revealing a wide shot of the scene and the distant cityscape.

This video is filmed from a high vantage point on a building. The background features a distant cityscape, while the foreground includes parts of the building. As the camera ascends, a man in orange enters from the bottom right, riding a bicycle. He jumps onto a stone railing and then lands on the grass below.

The video shows a person in red riding a bicycle and jumping from a high vantage point. In the top-left corner of the frame, there is a building on elevated ground, with grass below and a distant cityscape in the background. At first, the scene contains no visible person. Then, the individual appears from beneath the building, jumps onto the grass, and rides out of the frame through the bottom-right corner.

This video shows a person cycling near the sea, with a small blue boat and a seawall in the background. At first, the cyclist is on the left, and only the front half of the bike is visible, along with his hands and head. As he moves forward, his full body briefly shows, but soon, he rides up a dirt mound on the right and exits the frame from the top-right corner.

The video shows a man skateboarding in a tree-lined urban area, jumping onto a railing and then back to the ground. In the beginning, the frame only shows a small part of the cityscape. The man then enters the frame, and the camera tracks his movements, dynamically changing the shot size from a full shot when he first appears to a medium close-up by the end.

The video shows a man skateboarding. It starts with an extreme wide shot of him, and as he moves closer to the camera, his size gradually increases, transitioning to a full shot with dynamic size. Then, his upper body exits the frame, presenting a medium shot of him. As he moves further away from the camera, the shot returns to an extreme wide shot.
The scene begins with a full shot of a man and ends with a focus on his skateboard and legs.

The video begins with a medium shot focusing on a boy's lower body as he skateboards up a small slope. As he reaches the top, the camera tilts up and zooms in slightly, briefly transitioning to a full-body view. When the boy jumps down the slope, the camera captures only his upper body in a medium shot.

The video begins with a medium close-up of a Black woman wearing an American flag, speaking in an interview in a stadium. The camera then zooms out to reveal a group of Black women, all wearing American flags, showing their upper bodies. There is a hand holding a microphone in the foreground on the right of the frame, suggesting these Black women are being interviewed together.

The video shows a girl washing her hands in front of a mirror. It begins with a close-up of her turning on the faucet, showing only her arms and a small part of her body. The camera then tilts upward, revealing the chest-up body of the girl in the mirror and part of her head on the far right of the frame.

The video features a girl in front of a mirror, filmed over her shoulder. Initially, the reflection of the girl in the mirror is clear, showing her upper body, while part of her shoulder and her head in the foreground are blurred. As she turns to the left, the focus shifts to her, causing her reflection in the mirror to blur.
The video features two cartoon-style animated cats. The gray-blue character on the left is shown in a close-up of its head, while the red character on the right is shown in full body.
The video features two cartoon-style animated cats. The gray-blue character on the left is shown in a close-up of its head, while the red character on the right is shown in full body.

This is a medium shot showing the main character (Tom) in the center, flanked by smaller secondary characters (angel and devil versions of himself) positioned symmetrically on either side, both on small clouds, creating a balanced composition.

The video shows three cartoon cats in a real-world background. The gray-blue cartoon cat in the center takes up a large portion of the frame, with its head and half of its upper body visible, occupying about 80% of the frame's height. The white cartoon cat is on the left side of the frame, and the red cartoon cat is on the right side, both shown in full body, standing on clouds. In the final shot, both the white and red cartoon cats disappear, leaving only the gray-blue cartoon cat in the frame.

The video features two cartoon cats. It begins with a close-up of a gray-blue cartoon cat, followed by the appearance of a red cartoon cat on a cloud with a full body visible on the right side of the frame. The red cat then disappears, and the gray-blue cat moves to the right, likely to chase the red cat. In the final shot, only part of the gray-blue cat's body and an ear remain in the frame.

The video shows Tom chasing Jerry with dramatic changes in shot size. Tom first appears in a full-body shot as he jumps in from the side of the screen. He then puts Jerry in a bag. In the final moment, Tom attempts to jump down and exit the frame.

This shot features a medium, slightly high-angle view of a champagne bottle falling onto a textured, light green blanket. Initially, the frame contains only the bottle, but then the cartoon character Jerry, rendered in a classic style, jumps from the right to the left half of the frame, striking a playful pose with his arms out.

This video shows a scene from an animated cartoon where Tom the cat is trying to catch Jerry the mouse. At the beginning, Tom’s head and hands are visible at the bottom of the frame while Jerry’s full body is in view. The shot size changes frequently throughout the sequence — sometimes Tom’s full body is visible, other times only his head appears. Jerry is mostly shown in full. On average, the shot size can be described as a medium shot.

The video begins with a high-angle full shot of Jerry watching Tom midair as Tom falls to the ground along with the ceiling light. As Tom descends, the video shifts to Jerry spinning in midair, spreading his arms, and gracefully falling to the ground.

The video begins with a ground-level shot of an animated brown mouse (Jerry) standing in front of a door frame and running into a room through a partially open door. As the mouse slams the door shut, an animated blue cat (Tom)’s head collides with it, creating a large hole. Realistic door fragments burst outward, emphasizing the impact. The collision causes the mouse to bounce slightly upward in the frame before quickly scurrying away. The camera then shifts to focus on the cat’s angry head protruding through the hole in the door.

The video opens with a wide shot of a bustling street, showing a man in black wearing a duck-tongue hat leaping over a woman seated on a sedan chair carried by two bearers. The camera then follows him as he runs forward along the street, maintaining the full shot.

The video begins with a wide shot, showing two foreground characters in traditional Japanese attire—a man in a dark kimono with a partially shaved head on the left and a woman in a pink kimono on the right. Suddenly, a modern-dressed man wearing a black t-shirt, dark pants, and a baseball cap enters the background with a stunt jump into the traditional room. The composition then forms a triangular framing, emphasizing the contrast between the historical setting and the contemporary intruder.
The scene begins with a scenery shot, before a train enters the frame from the right side, occupying the entire frame until it disapears off screen to the left.

The video begins with a medium shot focused on the base of two bonsai trees. The camera then moves upward to reveal the tops of the trees. As the camera continues to move up, the bonsai trees nearly move out of the frame. Finally, the upper body of a man in red T-shirt appears in the background.

The video shows a full shot of a man in a red shirt and black jeans standing and talking to another man seated on a couch in a blue shirt, with only the upper body of the second man visible in the frame.

The video shows a man in brown clothing and a man in blue clothing in an indoor setting, with a background of trees and grass visible through a window. The scene starts with the man in brown standing on the left side of the frame, showing his body from the feet up, while the man in blue sits on the right side, showing his upper body. As the man in brown sits down, the camera descends, revealing both men sitting, with their bodies visible from the feet up.

The video features a full shot of a woman jumping into the air and performing two midair rotations, as if preparing to dive into the water. The background includes an Olympic sign, indicating the scene takes place indoors. The camera remains at a fixed angle, with the woman's full body visible only during the middle portion of the video.

The shot features three people, with two in focus. It begins with a blurry close-up of a man in the foreground, while the head of another person is clearly visible behind him. As the man in the foreground moves out of the frame, a medium shot of the two people kneeling on one knee is revealed, occupying nearly 100% of the frame's height.

The video is shot from a third-person over-the-shoulder POV, showing three characters. The right side of the frame remains a close-up of one character's back. On the left, the camera first shows a person lying on the ground, then tilts upward to reveal another standing person.

The video appears to be filmed from inside a car's trunk. Initially, the character's face is faintly visible through the car's left window. They then open the trunk, revealing a medium shot of themself, place a bag inside, and attempt to close the trunk. In the final frame, only their hand closing the trunk remains visible.

The video features a claymation set indoors, where humanoid characters socialize. It begins with a medium shot focusing on a character in the foreground. The focus then shifts to three characters in the middle ground behind them.

The video shows a wide shot of an outdoor experimental setup with several yellow structures, including a rotating crane holding a yellow toy plane, set against a backdrop of open fields and distant mountains. The crane rotates as the camera moves closer. Then, the toy plane hooks a white bag suspended in the air.

The video shows a wooden experimental setup in an outdoor setting. It focuses on part of the setup, with a ball rolling down from the top. On the left side of the frame, there’s an object covered with white fabric, and in the background on the right, mountains, fields, and the sky are visible.

The video showcases a snowy landscape with a wooden post in the foreground, positioned on the left side of the frame, and a snow-covered house and trees out of focus in the background on the right. Only the lower part of the wooden post is visible.

The first half of the video is a scenery shot, showing trees in a snowy landscape with the camera facing the sun, creating a halo in the center. The screen then fades to black, displaying a subtitle that gradually disappears.

The video is shot from a first-person POV, showing a scene of the elephant area at a zoo. It begins with three signs in the foreground, with an elephant visible in the background. The camera then moves to the right, revealing two more elephants in the distance. Then, a woman in pink enters the frame with her back turned, standing still, suggesting she is watching the elephants.

This video, shot from a first-person POV, shows a wide view of a park. The camera follows a man and a woman from behind as they walk forward, showing only their upper bodies from the knees up, leaving more content for the park's scenery.

The video is shot from a first-person POV, showing a zoo scene. It begins with a wide shot of three deer in a fenced area. The camera then pans left, revealing the upper body and backs of some people, suggesting they are looking at the deer. The camera continues panning left and moving forward, with the people exiting the frame and then reveals the zoo surroundings, including trees, a path, and a fence.

The video begins with a small rectangular window, through which a small red panda can be seen, though not clearly. The camera then pans left to reveal it is inside a zoo, showing some visitors and the zoo scenery in a wide shot.
This video is a first-person perspective shot through a diver’s mask. The frame shows the mask’s edges, the person’s hands, and the underwater scenery, making it difficult to determine the shot size.
